<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wạtẖq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (wạtẖq ạ̹ny hʿdy ạlbḥr mhmạ kạnt ạ̉mwạjh sẖdydh
 wạ̹n qạmwạ ʿly jnwd ạlsẖr mḥmy wrwḥy msẖ wḥydh)2
 wạ̉n ṭmrfy ạlạ̉rḍ ạ̹nt wạʿdny bạ̉rḍ jdydh
 ạlqrạr- wạtẖq fyk msẖ wạtẖq fy ạ̹nt ạ̹lh ṣạḥb ạlslṭạn
 wạ̹n tql ạlḥml ʿly ạ̹nt ạlly sẖạylh yạḥnạn
 (wạtẖq fyk ạ̉nạ wạtẖq fyk wạtẖq fyk msẖ wạtẖq fy)2
 2- (wạtẖq ạ̉nạ hạdy wmrtạḥ mfdy wạ̹bn mlk ạlmlwk
 dạfʿ fy ạ̉lm wjrạḥ wdm ʿ ạlṣlyb msfwk)2
 dạ ạ̉bwyạ wf ḥḍnh ạ̉rtạḥ bʿd mạ knt ʿbd wmmlwk
 3- (wạtẖq ạ̹ny ạ̉nạ mḥbwb ly ạ̹lh ḥbh ʿjyb
 byḥbny wạ̉nạ kly ʿywb kẖạṭy byqwly yạ ḥbyb)2
 bymḥy wygẖfr kl ạldẖnwb bs ạ̉nạ ạ̉ṭlb whw yjyb</lyrics>
<author>tạmr jwrj, ạ̹yhạb fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>6952</hymn_number>
</song>